docs {
  # List Vendors

  Returns all hardware vendors in the system.

  ## Data Shape

  ```json
  [
    {
      "id": "nvidia",
      "name": "NVIDIA",
      "description": "GPU and AI computing company",
      "website": "https://nvidia.com"
    }
  ]
  ```

  ## Fields

  | Field | Type | Description |
  |-------|------|-------------|
  | id | string | Unique vendor identifier |
  | name | string | Display name of the vendor |
  | description | string | Brief description of the vendor |
  | website | string | Vendor's website URL |

  ## Query Parameters

  | Param | Description |
  |-------|-------------|
  | _sort | Field to sort by (e.g., `name`) |
  | _order | Sort order: `asc` or `desc` |
  | _page | Page number for pagination |
  | _limit | Items per page |

  ## Response Headers

  - `X-Total-Count`: Total number of items (when using pagination)
}
